Broadway, east side, from W. 102nd (right not seen) to 105th (left) as viewed northeastward from the S.W. corner of Broadway and 102nd Street.  The low structures in the center occupy the 103rd to 104th Streets frontage.  Note the subway kiosk at 103rd Street.

1937.

Anonymous gift.

Neg. #2842
